  "engines": [
    "Obrix"
  ],
  "description": "Low drone architecture: Sine octave-down + Triangle at standard pitch, fmDepth 0.35 for gentle cross-modulation that adds warmth without destroying the fundamental. driftRate 0.003 (the slowest allowed) and driftDepth 0.72 with journeyMode=1.0 \u2014 the Journey Paradox at maximum: the sound evolves over minutes, not seconds. At 0.003 Hz drift rate, a full drift cycle takes 5 minutes. The drone you play at noon will be subtly different at sunset. Poly 4 to stack harmonics. proc1=LP at 350 Hz for sub-bass body.",
